Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.67,0:01:23.55,OP jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Listen to my song…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.18,0:01:36.43,OP jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}僕の聲は聞こえていますか？　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:39.09,OP jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Please tell me…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.26,0:01:42.40,OP jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}答えのない虚構の空目指し　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:44.67,OP jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Fly far away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.77,0:01:47.75,OP jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}言葉じゃ足りないから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:50.73,OP jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}僕のすべて受け止めて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.82,0:01:53.80,OP jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}制禦できない…したくないよ　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:01:59.61,OP jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}初めて知る感覚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.24,0:02:05.97,OP jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}君に歌うよ　永遠の始まりを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:07.91,OP jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}「だから笑って…」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:13.18,OP jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}誰よりも熱く誰よりも強く抱き締めるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:16.47,OP jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}震える心　揺さぶればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:19.02,OP jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}何かが動きます
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:22.71,OP jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}僕等きっと、生まれた日から
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:26.77,OP jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}出會える日をずっと探してたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:29.81,OP jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}風の鳴く夜は思い出して　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.89,0:02:34.72,OP jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}共に奏でた奇跡　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.77,0:02:38.12,OP jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}天に舞うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.67,0:01:23.55,OP cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}{\fnDFGSNGyoSho-W5\fs40}Listen to my song…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.18,0:01:36.43,OP cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}能听见我的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:39.09,OP cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}{\fnDFGSNGyoSho-W5\fs40}Please tell me…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.26,0:01:42.40,OP cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}以找不到答案的虚构苍空为目标
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:44.67,OP cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}{\fnDFGSNGyoSho-W5\fs40}Fly far away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.77,0:01:47.75,OP cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}光是话语还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:50.73,OP cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}请接受我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.82,0:01:53.80,OP cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}无法控制…也不想控制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:01:59.61,OP cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}初次体会到的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.24,0:02:05.97,OP cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}向你歌唱永远的序曲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:07.66,OP cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}「所以欢笑吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:13.18,OP cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}比谁都热情 比谁都用力的拥抱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:16.47,OP cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}颤抖的心灵就让它颤抖即可
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:19.02,OP cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}有什么在涌动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:22.71,OP cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}我们一定从诞生之日起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:26.77,OP cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}到相遇的那天都一直寻找着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:29.81,OP cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}回想起那风鸣之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.89,0:02:34.72,OP cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}一起奏响的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.77,0:02:38.12,OP cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}舞动在空中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:30.15,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Get back to where
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.25,0:22:31.82,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I once belonged, BUT!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:35.69,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}振り向けば 風の音だけ　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:36.95,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Don't let me down　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.07,0:22:38.45,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Don't make me confuse
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:43.58,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}絶望が塗り潰してく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.87,0:22:45.41,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Escape from here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.48,0:22:47.24,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}It's like a nightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:49.88,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}追いかけてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:53.60,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}夢も　理想も　情熱も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.71,0:22:57.13,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}またかき消されて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.21,0:23:00.18,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}哀しい日々は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:03.77,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}いつかは終わりが来るの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.81,0:23:06.61,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}迷いながら　もがきながら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.89,0:23:12.59,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}それでも　まだあきらめたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.83,0:23:14.53,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}傷だらけでも　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:19.53,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}この手のひらに 決して消えない星がある 　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.60,0:23:22.88,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}流れて堕ちた光は今も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.98,0:23:26.66,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}あの場所を遠く照らしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.77,0:23:29.95,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}何度でも手を伸ばそう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.07,0:23:33.13,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}今は描けなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.25,0:23:36.24,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}信じることが強さに変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.31,0:23:39.78,ED jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}輝いてよ　Shooting STAR
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:30.15,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Get back to where
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.25,0:22:31.82,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I once belonged, BUT!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:35.69,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}转身遥望 只有风声　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:36.95,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Don't let me down　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.07,0:22:38.45,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Don't make me confuse
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:43.58,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}将绝望掩盖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.87,0:22:45.41,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Escape from here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.48,0:22:47.24,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}It's like a nightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:49.88,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}正在追逐着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:53.60,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}梦想　理想　热情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.71,0:22:57.13,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}也全都消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.21,0:23:00.18,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}悲伤的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:03.77,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}会不会有结束之日？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.81,0:23:06.61,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}迷惘着 挣扎着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.89,0:23:12.59,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}即使如此 也还不想放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.83,0:23:14.53,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}即使伤痕累累
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:19.53,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}在手中 仍有绝不会消失的星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.60,0:23:22.88,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}滑落之后 那光芒现在也 　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.98,0:23:26.66,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}依然远远地照耀着那里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.77,0:23:29.95,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}无数次伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.07,0:23:33.13,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}即使现在无法描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.25,0:23:36.24,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}信任会化为力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.31,0:23:39.78,ED cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}闪耀吧 Shooting STAR
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.49,0:00:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.86,0:00:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天不用当班 打算骑电单车远行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是刚拿到的驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.22,0:00:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来任务以外的时候听到翼唱歌还是头一回呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.15,0:00:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样子感觉不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再让我听你哼歌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼歌不是让人听的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.49,0:00:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦 那么我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.20,0:00:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:00:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检查完毕了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,损伤完全恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了 奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:44.68,title3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs64\blur4\fad(500,0)\an5\pos(1064,440)}第九话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:44.68,title3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs64\blur4\fad(500,0)\an5\pos(1064,500)}战士之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校正下方居然有这样的防空壕和地下基地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.12,0:02:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位好像是协助人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.41,0:02:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是小日向未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.27,0:03:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为立花是这种性格 我想会为你带来很多麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是请你要支持她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 因为响是个残念的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给您添麻烦了 请您多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说来往于响的客套话 两人都很意气相投
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.75,0:03:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉被人耍了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变了 还是被改变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过和未来一起在这里感觉有点难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.62,0:03:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让小日向作为外部协助人 登录进二课的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是司令安排的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过可能会给你带来不便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听过说明了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会不便呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来师傅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也在找他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:03:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Girls Talk
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很迷惘该吐槽哪里好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之别无视我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了子小姐也对那种有兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了我的恋花百物语 晚上可会睡不着的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直像怪谈一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了子小姐的恋爱故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是让人沉醉 华丽的 成熟女人一般的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是很久以前的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看人家这样 我可是惊人地专一哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为樱井女士比起恋爱会更专注于研究
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是俗话说“生命短暂 少女要尽情恋爱”嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且女孩的恋爱力量是很大的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“女孩”吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会开始研究圣遗物本来也是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:05:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 我也很忙的 可不能在这里偷懒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是你自己插嘴进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪川先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎样 能干的女人的条件是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据谈一场恋爱的好坏决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子们要谈一场好的恋爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没机会听了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留课题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是总有一天我要打探出了子小姐的浪漫史
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了些不像我会说的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是 被改变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 还没回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要向他报告健康检查的结果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个行程时间快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经开始有工作了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点点来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只是练手罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不是以前那样的紧密日程了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 翼小姐 我们去约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没带帮手来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,0:07:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为被任命去保护你的 只有我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么知道这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原公安特工 已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是慰劳品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没放
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小提琴家雪音正纪和妻子歌唱家索妮特雪音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.07,0:07:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八年前在救济难民的活动中 被卷进战火中死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下的女儿也行踪不明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后因联合国军的介入 形势改变
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:08:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被当地组织抓走的女儿被发现后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移送到了日本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查得很清楚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种调查真让人想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时的我们为了寻找适合者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意力都放在音乐界的名门
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为孤身一人的少女的容身之处 给了她一片天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 这里也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 少女在回国后不久就杳无音信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也很慌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多二课的搜查员被驱赶了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分跟这件事有关的人都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者以行踪不明这种糟透的结局拉上帷幕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干什么啊 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想做的 就是救出你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成接受了的工作 是大人的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人的职责？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了多余的事以外 什么都不肯做的大人说得真好听
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得您可能已经猜到 响睡过头就是原因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人看来非常期待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想把某人迟到而失去的时间补回来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说翼小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼小姐要的布偶我立花响一定抓到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过会不会对游戏过于认真了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别发出奇怪的声音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这台娃娃机坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也许被诅咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都坏了 继续破坏也没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要装备symphogear
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我和平地解决啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任凭愤怒爆发的话 武器也能…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别大声叫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那么想大声叫的话 我带你去个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:44.25,NETA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注：卡拉OK街
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.53,0:11:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.38,0:11:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有幸能和顶级歌手一起来卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想这样做一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好古雅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.69,0:12:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个为什么那么精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是翼小姐不给力啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天做了太多不习惯的事情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为战士 早就决定奉献给战场了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天感觉看到的净是没见过的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 立花你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里就是碰头的公园
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起玩过的地方 还有没玩过的地方都是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼小姐所知道的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为昨天翼小姐为了我们而战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.32,0:13:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才有今天这个大家一起生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请不要说自己不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗的背后之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那对面会不会又有其他不同的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是这么想的 也是为了看这个而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.82,0:13:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 这就是奏所看到的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复出演唱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艺术节原本要在十天后举行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是挤到那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为因我倒下而中止的Live的补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼小姐 这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对立花来说 也是有着痛苦回忆的会场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.86,0:14:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么痛苦 也绝对要克服过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩排的感觉不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tony·Glaser
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.16,0:15:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,METRO MUSIC的制作人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前提出翼小姐的海外发展的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为怎么说都不肯理我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就直接过来交涉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr Glaser
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于那件事 我们正式地…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再给我些时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说你的想法正在改变？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.14,0:15:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 如果是你现在所得出的答案 请务必告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的Live 我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:16:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得拿到了票
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会错过开演
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我是响
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(602,668)} Noise
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦测到噪音出现的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.06,0:16:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼我待会就联络…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.59,0:16:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现场请让我一个人去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望今天的翼小姐能专心属于自己的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让她在那个会场唱到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.04,0:16:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互不相欠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能尽情地歌唱 感觉真好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的感觉真的久违了 我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是记起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么喜欢唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢在愿意听我唱歌的大家面前歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许大家都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想到大海的彼岸去唱歌吗 这样的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在迷茫 自己是为了什么而唱歌的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我希望能有更多的人听我唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使语言不通
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.63,0:20:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果有通过唱歌能传达的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望世界上的所有人听我唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我坚信我的歌声能拯救他人而一路唱了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 接下来我希望将自己融入到大家之中来唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是这么地喜欢唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我唯一的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.66,0:20:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会原谅的 理所当然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.75,0:21:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr Glaser
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.75,0:21:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点快 今晚就先退场了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.78,0:21:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为接下来可能会很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.30,0:21:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风鸣翼的梦想就拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.03,0:21:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙可是敌人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么我会救她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 菲尼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.88,0:21:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
